Class Main

  • java.lang.Object
    • HW4.Main
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Control

    public class Main
extends java.lang.Object
    Frame class for the graphical user interface of connect five. Controller for handling interactions between the view components and the model.
    Author:
    Edgar Padilla, Oscar Galindo, Mario Delgado:
